Quick note: FZ doesn't have a spark.

::FZ::

FZ dives to the side, barely avoiding Angel Prime's blade. He flips 
out his missile launcher, firing a glowing missile at the Maximal.

(FZ's missiles glow with energy as they fly, so laser shots bounce 
off. Explosions would take them out, though, and so would meelee 
weapons. When they explode, they create an energy field 6 feet in 
diameter which drains the energy of anything they touch. FZ can 
remote-detonate the missiles, so he'll try to get them as close to 
Angel Prime as he can)
